title: Guilty Conscience 2

description.plain:
“Guilty Conscience 2” is the sequel to Eminem’s popular 1999 track “Guilty Conscience.” The original track focuses on Slim Shady influencing different people to do morally wrong things while Dr. Dre attempts to do the opposite, making them do better actions.

On the other hand, the sequel is written as a conversation/argument between Eminem and his alter ego, Slim Shady.
